      <title>欧洲监管机构暗示支持德国商业银行可能达成的交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-14/european-regulators-signal-backing-for-possible-commerzbank-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[多位央行和监管部门高级官员表示，意大利联合信贷银行（UniCredit SpA）对竞争对手德国商业银行（Commerzbank AG）的潜在收购可能会获得监管部门的批准，并称几乎没有理由认为这笔交易会引起担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-14/european-regulators-signal-backing-for-possible-commerzbank-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 14 Oct 2024 09:19:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国信贷扩张超出预期但贷款表现令人失望</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-14/china-s-credit-expansion-tops-forecasts-but-loans-disappoint</link>
      <description><![CDATA[受国债销量激增推动，中国9月份信贷扩张超出预期，但新增贷款表现令人失望，因国内需求依然疲软。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-14/china-s-credit-expansion-tops-forecasts-but-loans-disappoint</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 14 Oct 2024 09:17:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
